kdal (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * kdalc compiler: lexer, parser, semantic analysis, C code generator.
  * kdality CLI: compile, init, simulate, lint, test-gen, dt-gen, kdalctl.
  * Standard library: uart, spi, i2c, gpio, gpu, npu device headers.
  * CMake build system with find_package(KDAL) support.
  * Public kernel-space headers and compiler headers.

